00:21:32.810 --> 00:21:36.210
improved by 23% for the group
that saw stress as enhancing,

00:21:36.210 --> 00:21:38.610
a nearly 30% increase
in their productivity,

00:21:38.610 --> 00:21:40.240
and their levels of
happiness improved.

00:21:40.240 --> 00:21:43.250
