00:58:56.710 --> 00:58:58.360
Pick up a positive habit.

00:58:58.360 --> 00:59:00.660
Get involved with
one of these programs

00:59:00.660 --> 00:59:02.649
to create one of these
positive changes.

00:59:02.649 --> 00:59:04.440
Because what we find
is that it ripples out

00:59:04.440 --> 00:59:07.160
so much to effect other people.

00:59:07.160 --> 00:59:07.980
Real quick story.

00:59:07.980 --> 00:59:11.769
I was working with a CEO
of a fast food company.

00:59:11.769 --> 00:59:14.060
He sold his company for
hundreds of millions of dollars

00:59:14.060 --> 00:59:15.140
and had a breakdown.

00:59:15.140 --> 00:59:16.590
He made millions of dollars.

00:59:16.590 --> 00:59:19.870
But that night he went
on track with his wife

00:59:19.870 --> 00:59:22.787
and start walking off some of
the weight that he had gained

00:59:22.787 --> 00:59:25.120
and talking about things that
he was grateful for, doing

00:59:25.120 --> 00:59:25.953
that positive habit.

00:59:25.953 --> 00:59:28.292
It was so helpful that they
start doing it and telling

00:59:28.292 --> 00:59:29.750
their kids that
they were doing it.

00:59:29.750 --> 00:59:32.207
And they got a call from one
of their friend's parents

00:59:32.207 --> 00:59:34.540
who said, did you hear what
happened at the summer party

00:59:34.540 --> 00:59:35.510
for your daughter?

00:59:35.510 --> 00:59:36.635
And they were like, oh, no.

00:59:36.635 --> 00:59:38.110
Was there drinking or boys?

00:59:38.110 --> 00:59:42.426
And they said, no, she got
everyone in her friend group

00:59:42.426 --> 00:59:44.050
to sit around and
talk about the things

00:59:44.050 --> 00:59:46.425
that they were grateful for
that were going on at school.

00:59:46.425 --> 00:59:48.910
We can actually create a
different social script

00:59:48.910 --> 00:59:51.234
for the world where people
don't wait for happiness off

00:59:51.234 --> 00:59:53.150
in the future but actually
are creating it now

00:59:53.150 --> 00:59:55.320
and actually are
tipping this world away

00:59:55.320 --> 00:59:57.380
from negativity and
stress to a world that

00:59:57.380 --> 01:00:00.040
believes this behavior matters
and can see ways of changing

01:00:00.040 --> 01:00:02.910
this reality into a better
reality for all of us,

01:00:02.910 --> 01:00:04.070
which is why I get excited.

